# FleetOps Mobile App

Placeholder for React Native mobile application.

## Setup

```bash
cd mobile
npx create-expo-app FleetOpsMobile --template blank-typescript
cd FleetOpsMobile
npm install @react-navigation/native @react-navigation/stack
npm install react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context
npm install @react-native-async-storage/async-storage
npm install axios
```

## Features to Build
- Dashboard overview
- Task management
- Approval workflow
- Push notifications
- Biometric auth
